@startuml
title Activity Diagram: User Journey - Dashboard to Risk Result
skinparam ConditionEndStyle hline
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor White
skinparam ActivityBorderColor Blue
skinparam ArrowColor Blue

|User|
start
:Log in & Enter **Dashboard**;

|Frontend/System|
:Display Active Ferry Routes;
:Fetch Preliminary Status;

|User|
:Selects a Ferry Route;
:Clicks **"View Forecast"**;

|Backend & AI|
:Retrieve Weather Data;
:Calculate **Risk Score** (AI);
note right
  Safe / Caution / High Risk
end note

|Frontend/System|
if (Risk is High?) then (Yes)
  :Display **RED Alert**;
  :Show "Cancellation Likely";
else (No)
  :Display **GREEN Badge**;
  :Show "Safe to Travel";
endif

|User|
:Make Travel Decision;
stop

@enduml
